779
00:36:11,300 --> 00:36:12,140
Oh.

780
00:36:12,660 --> 00:36:13,820
Block him right away.

781
00:36:14,140 --> 00:36:15,580
He'll probably bother you again.

782
00:36:16,300 --> 00:36:17,170
No.

783
00:36:17,220 --> 00:36:18,740
Maybe keeping him could be useful.

784
00:36:18,900 --> 00:36:19,900
Useful? How so?

785
00:36:21,020 --> 00:36:21,930
Then, sis,

786
00:36:21,930 --> 00:36:23,660
did he ever bother you on WeChat?

787
00:36:25,620 --> 00:36:26,460
Who?

788
00:36:26,980 --> 00:36:28,700
That cool guy who was with you yesterday.

789
00:36:29,500 --> 00:36:30,340
No.

790
00:36:31,500 --> 00:36:32,340
I don't have

791
00:36:32,340 --> 00:36:33,540
