792
00:36:41,300 --> 00:36:42,460
Who's it?

793
00:36:43,780 --> 00:36:44,620
(Jiang Yifan)
(Don't reply)

794
00:36:44,780 --> 00:36:45,620
(to that girl's)

795
00:36:45,810 --> 00:36:46,660
(any message.)

796
00:36:46,660 --> 00:36:48,020
Could it be…

797
00:36:50,900 --> 00:36:52,180
(Mud Buddha)
(Getting jealous?)

798
00:36:53,180 --> 00:36:54,940
(Jiang Yifan)
(Don't overthink it. Not jealous.)

799
00:36:57,220 --> 00:36:58,620
(Then why?)

800
00:37:01,060 --> 00:37:03,700
(Mud Buddha: Then why?)

801
00:37:03,880 --> 00:37:04,920
(Jiang Yifan)
(No reason.)

802
00:37:07,140 --> 00:37:07,980
(Do not reply.)

803
00:37:22,860 --> 00:37:23,700
Bei,

804
00:37:24,020 --> 00:37:25,380
I suddenly really want to eat

805
00:37:25,380 --> 00:37:26,820
those meat floss buns from next door.

806
00:37:27,100 --> 00:37:28,220
Can you buy me some?

807
00:37:28,980 --> 00:37:29,820
Sure.

808
00:37:30,340 --> 00:37:31,260
What do you want?

809
00:37:32,580 --> 00:37:34,740
I heard their sweetheart pastry's good.

810
00:37:35,380 --> 00:37:36,220
One will be enough.

811
00:37:39,180 --> 00:37:40,340
Okay, I'll go get it for you.

812
00:37:40,860 --> 00:37:41,700
Mm.

813
00:37:51,340 --> 00:37:52,180
Sis.

814
00:37:52,340 --> 00:37:53,180
Mm.

815
00:37:53,460 --> 00:37:54,740
You're not mad, right?

816
00:37:56,900 --> 00:37:58,060
Why would I be mad?

817
00:37:58,660 --> 00:38:00,700
I was afraid you'd misunderstand about us.

818
00:38:02,020 --> 00:38:02,860
I'm actually not

819
00:38:02,860 --> 00:38:04,340
very confident most of the time.

820
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:07,900
Honestly, I was a bit worried before I came.

821
00:38:08,860 --> 00:38:09,940
But after seeing you,

822
00:38:09,940 --> 00:38:11,260
I'm completely relieved.

823
00:38:12,100 --> 00:38:13,740
You're so sweet, warm,

824
00:38:13,740 --> 00:38:15,020
genuine, not fake at all.

825
00:38:15,340 --> 00:38:17,180
If someone said you'd come between a couple,

826
00:38:17,820 --> 00:38:19,100
I'd never believe it.

827
00:38:19,420 --> 00:38:20,540
Of course I wouldn't.

828
00:38:22,380 --> 00:38:24,220
But if he ever becomes single,

829
00:38:24,220 --> 00:38:25,180
that's hard to say.

830
00:38:25,620 --> 00:38:26,660
Maybe

831
00:38:27,140 --> 00:38:28,260
he's in a bad mood,

832
00:38:28,500 --> 00:38:29,700
and decides to marry someone,

833
00:38:29,780 --> 00:38:30,940
then maybe I'll get my chance.

834
00:38:38,180 --> 00:38:39,340
I'm kidding.

835
00:38:45,300 --> 00:38:46,620
Be more confident. You're great.

836
00:38:47,700 --> 00:38:48,740
Just won't get the chance.

837
00:38:53,170 --> 00:38:54,020
Mm.

838
00:38:54,020 --> 00:38:54,860
I know.

839
00:38:55,300 --> 00:38:56,660
You're totally his type.

840
00:39:00,540 --> 00:39:01,540
You really know him.

841
00:39:01,580 --> 00:39:02,420
Yeah.

842
00:39:02,700 --> 00:39:04,300
We've known each other for five...

843
00:39:04,620 --> 00:39:05,460
Mhm.

844
00:39:05,620 --> 00:39:06,820
No, six years.

845
00:39:08,340 --> 00:39:09,380
I'm super close with him.

846
00:39:11,380 --> 00:39:13,100
So if there's anything I don't get,

847
00:39:13,660 --> 00:39:14,700
I'll come to you for help.

848
00:39:15,100 --> 00:39:15,940
Sure.

849
00:39:18,860 --> 00:39:20,460
Has he ever mentioned

850
00:39:21,140 --> 00:39:22,100
things about the UK?

851
00:39:23,580 --> 00:39:24,740
You mean

852
00:39:25,500 --> 00:39:27,540
when he lived with you and your boyfriend?

853
00:39:27,540 --> 00:39:28,900
Ex-boyfriend.

854
00:39:30,820 --> 00:39:31,980
You wouldn't get it.

855
00:39:33,140 --> 00:39:35,540
That feeling when I've just decided to be

856
00:39:35,820 --> 00:39:38,180
with someone and then meet a guy who feels

857
00:39:38,780 --> 00:39:39,620
like my Mr. Right.

858
00:39:40,580 --> 00:39:42,180
(YM. Cake)

859
00:39:47,020 --> 00:39:50,340
Happy birthday to you.

860
00:39:51,020 --> 00:39:54,620
Happy birthday to you.

861
00:39:55,460 --> 00:39:59,260
Happy birthday to you.

862
00:40:00,100 --> 00:40:03,460
Happy birthday to you.

863
00:40:07,300 --> 00:40:09,300
